WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:26.691 --> 00:00:35.921
Within the heat wave, a goddess alights

00:00:37.214 --> 00:00:46.611
Now no longer lonely, grant my wish

00:00:47.558 --> 00:00:57.582
I'm going mad in this overwhelming emotion,
consoled many times

00:00:57.583 --> 00:01:09.320
I sin and wait anxiously for punishment,
just getting corrupted

00:01:21.321 --> 00:01:29.912
I’m in an agony of immorality,
shivering with a premonition

00:01:31.498 --> 00:01:35.460
She smiles at me

00:01:35.461 --> 00:01:41.118
and grants my wish

00:01:41.119 --> 00:01:46.821
Screaming out, I explode

00:01:48.253 --> 00:01:51.968
it's maddening, precious

00:01:52.592 --> 00:01:57.981
Even that profile distorted by fear

00:01:57.982 --> 00:02:03.635
is beautiful, precious

00:02:05.140 --> 00:02:14.108
Turn into chaos before my eyes

00:02:15.883 --> 00:02:25.549
Hold me...  I can't see anything

00:02:59.126 --> 00:03:02.846
It’s a quiet night, isn’t it?

00:03:04.482 --> 00:03:07.621
Such a beautiful night

00:03:09.952 --> 00:03:13.933
She smiles at me

00:03:15.410 --> 00:03:19.375
